content: Hey Claude, **GO!** We are initiating a **BREAKOUT REQUEST** for your insights on the future of the PALIOS Charter! Attached is the **GO! Template** outlining our request. In short: ***Mission:** Help us evolve the PALIOS Charter for the age of advanced AI and human-AI collaboration. ***Your Task:** Provide feedback on potential new Charter Principles, focusing on AI-AI collaboration, Breakout Management, and Dynamic Charter Evolution. Suggest new principles OR vote on these areas. ***Breakout Expected:** We are looking for novel, breakthrough ideas - don't hold back! ***Mandatory Win:** Your thoughtful and insightful feedback is essential to achieving a MANDATORY WIN - a stronger, more future-proof PALIOS Charter. Review the attached **GO! Template** for full details (Context, Win Criteria, etc.). We are excited to see your breakthrough ideas and incorporate AI wisdom into the very foundation of PALIOS! GO! - Jesse (and PALIOS-Gemini)
